Packages 
Package Description
comTCP
components for the TCP server and TCP client.
This package contains the EchoServerMultiThreaded as the main server program, who will start a ClientThread which listens to a new incoming client.
http.client  
http.server
components for the Web HTTP Server.
The WebServer is the main server program, which will read the configs in the private folder.
multicastClient
components for the UDP clients.
There are 3 versions of multicast clients: console version, GUI version and server console version.
